Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.09,0:01:55.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Could there possibly be a demon\nwho can duplicate the Sacred Jewel?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.87,0:01:57.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.47,0:02:02.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha shattered\nthe Jewel!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.67,0:02:06.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fool! The Sacred Jewel\nwouldn't break so easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.54,0:02:09.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But I sensed the same presence\nas a Sacred Jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.51,0:02:13.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's an imitation Sacred Jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.48,0:02:18.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There is a demon trying to\nduplicate the Sacred Jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.62,0:02:23.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Jewel may be inferior\nto the real Sacred Jewel,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.83,0:02:25.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}but it still empowers\ndemons with more strength.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.10,0:02:31.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This aura is probably toxic to humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.73,0:02:33.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's an evil spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.24,0:02:35.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It will defile the human soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.31,0:02:39.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's probably the power of\nthe Sacred Jewel.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.69,0:02:50.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's daybreak.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.93,0:03:05.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So you've regained consciousness?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.10,0:03:08.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-What happened to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.24,0:03:10.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You were buried in the soil.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.97,0:03:11.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.67,0:03:13.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It was difficult digging you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.88,0:03:16.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Especially since we were injured, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.21,0:03:18.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What happened to Kagome?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.18,0:03:20.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.42,0:03:23.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome seems to have been\nkidnapped by that Bull Demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.09,0:03:25.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.39,0:03:28.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha went on ahead in\npursuit of Kagome.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.63,0:03:32.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now then, we must go, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.80,0:03:34.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Uh-huh, let's hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.57,0:03:37.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.50,0:03:41.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The bull's scent was so strong...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.40,0:03:43.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where'd it disappear to?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.07,0:03:46.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't smell Kagome either.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.64,0:03:47.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}All that's left is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.08,0:03:53.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.18,0:04:00.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If we kill you, Orochidayu\nwill give us more Sacred Jewels!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.36,0:04:02.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So die, half-demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.69,0:04:06.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.04,0:04:15.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't take us lightly, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.67,0:04:18.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We have Sacred Jewels!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.87,0:04:20.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.41,0:04:22.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll destroy you along\nwith your Sacred Jewels!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.83,0:04:39.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.43,0:04:42.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}We battled that Bull Demon and...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.20,0:04:44.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everyone?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.37,0:04:45.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where's everyone?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.15,0:05:01.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Looks so yummy... so yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.08,0:05:02.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.22,0:05:04.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Frog Demon of Tsukumo!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.69,0:05:06.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}And that boy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.16,0:05:07.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.10,0:05:20.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.84,0:05:22.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Izumo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.87,0:05:23.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.51,0:05:26.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.51,0:05:28.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes. I'm so glad you're okay, Izumo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.55,0:05:31.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The demons have ordered me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.31,0:05:36.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,to use my knowledge to create\nnot a fake Sacred Jewel,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.95,0:05:38.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but a real Sacred Jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.32,0:05:40.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.59,0:05:44.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It seems they've also been studying\nup on the Sacred Jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.46,0:05:47.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's right!\NThe Sacred Jewel shards!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.06,0:05:49.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Good, they're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.53,0:05:51.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.63,0:05:54.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're probably thinking\nthere's no escape from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.97,0:05:59.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Their workplace and mansion\nare just beyond here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.74,0:06:01.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.34,0:06:02.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.71,0:06:06.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The villagers have been captured\nby the Frog Demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.78,0:06:09.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We have to rescue them before\nhe eats their souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.55,0:06:12.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even if we don't have weapons?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.76,0:06:14.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're right.\NWe must find something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.49,0:06:18.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Frog Demon's weakness\nis fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.84,0:06:28.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shippo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.14,0:06:36.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They keep coming\none after another!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.35,0:06:43.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Go on! Or you won't\nget your reward!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.37,0:07:05.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Those who distinguish\nthemselves in battle
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.11,0:07:07.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,will be rewarded\nwith a real Sacred Jewel!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.09,0:07:26.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I was told to use this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.00,0:07:29.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you going to obey\nthose demons?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.77,0:07:33.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If that is the only way\nto stay alive... it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.44,0:07:37.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sure Inuyasha will come\nto rescue us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.87,0:07:42.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Aren't you interested in\nthe Sacred Jewel?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.75,0:07:43.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Interested?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.05,0:07:45.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You must have a wish that\nyou want granted
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.02,0:07:48.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,with the power of the Sacred Jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.42,0:07:50.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hmm... Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.09,0:07:54.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I want to retrieve the shards\nthat Naraku has.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.82,0:07:57.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But I have to do that myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.76,0:08:01.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We should check inside the mansion.\NWill you help?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.63,0:08:05.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sure. I hope we can build a fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.40,0:08:05.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.81,0:08:16.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn! There's no end to this!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.85,0:08:17.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Found him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.89,0:08:25.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let 'em come!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.43,0:08:35.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They've gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.87,0:08:39.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But we can't stay here\nlike this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.37,0:08:40.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm worried about Kagome.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.97,0:08:46.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So am I. But we must rest a little\nor we'll collapse.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.01,0:08:50.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Found 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.51,0:08:51.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.21,0:08:53.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's go, Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.15,0:08:54.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.78,0:08:57.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why isn't there anything\nwe can use?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.72,0:09:00.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is terrible for\na demon's mansion!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.06,0:09:01.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.03,0:09:06.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Izumo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.03,0:09:10.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Sacred Jewel was borne out of\nthe immense spiritual powers
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.87,0:09:12.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,of a priestess named Midoriko.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.80,0:09:13.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.60,0:09:15.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, I've heard that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.14,0:09:20.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It was created during a battle\nbetween Midoriko and demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.84,0:09:23.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Midoriko tried to destroy the demons
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.61,0:09:26.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and the demons tried to\ndestroy Midoriko.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.15,0:09:30.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The souls of the two sides were captured\nand became one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.49,0:09:32.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.89,0:09:34.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The pure soul of the priestess, Midoriko,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.79,0:09:41.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and the evil souls of the demons\nare intermingled in the Sacred Jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.66,0:09:47.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The imitation Sacred Jewels had\nhuman and demon souls sealed within.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.97,0:09:48.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.90,0:09:50.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That is not enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.31,0:09:55.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aramitama, Nigimitama,\NKushimitama, Sakimitama.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.25,0:10:00.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,In other words, courage, friendship,\nknowledge and love are necessary
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.22,0:10:03.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,in order for the Sacred Jewel\nto attain true power.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.79,0:10:05.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Izumo?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.53,0:10:12.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Kagome?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.47,0:10:23.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They're gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.21,0:10:25.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It'll be dark shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.94,0:10:28.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The birds did not fear\nthe dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.94,0:10:31.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I am the one who\nfears the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.78,0:10:34.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And those birds\nfear me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.42,0:10:37.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Umm... Izumo?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.62,0:10:40.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Izumo was my father's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.39,0:10:44.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He had scholarship and excelled\nin poetry and writing...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.36,0:10:46.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He loved flowers and birds.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.03,0:10:49.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Izumo was my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.90,0:10:50.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.51,0:10:59.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.38,0:11:03.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The name my mother gave me...\nis Gyu-oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.71,0:11:04.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.15,0:11:08.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That was my appearance\nduring the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.49,0:11:19.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is my appearance at night!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.66,0:11:21.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A half-demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.80,0:11:26.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Exactly... Kagome.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.14,0:11:30.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.51,0:11:33.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.61,0:11:36.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,As you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.38,0:11:38.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,By day, I appear as a man\nlike my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.15,0:11:40.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But at night,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.25,0:11:42.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I am a bull demon\nlike my mother was.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.18,0:11:45.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,In order to free myself from\nthis half-demon fate...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.15,0:11:47.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I will create a real Sacred Jewel!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.32,0:11:50.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So it was all your doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.66,0:11:52.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Have you been deceiving us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.16,0:11:58.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I traveled to many countries\nto learn about the Sacred Jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.57,0:12:00.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That is how I found out\nabout you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.17,0:12:05.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,With your souls, I can create\na Sacred Jewel!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.91,0:12:08.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Our... what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.18,0:12:09.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Priestess!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.58,0:12:12.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Your spirit and those Sacred\NJewel shards
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.18,0:12:15.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,will form the basis of\nthe new Sacred Jewel!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.98,0:12:18.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,However, that is not enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.22,0:12:20.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hence, I must collect more spirits!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.93,0:12:28.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The spirit of courage will come\nfrom that half-demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.50,0:12:38.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The spirit of knowledge will come\nfrom that priest!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.47,0:12:40.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hiraikotsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.21,0:12:47.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The spirit of love will come\nfrom that slayer!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.82,0:12:51.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku! Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.65,0:12:53.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Run into that valley!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.89,0:12:57.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And the spirit of friendship will\ncome from that little fox demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.36,0:12:59.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The four spirits will become\nthe divine good...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.06,0:13:02.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and I SHALL create a Sacred Jewel!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.17,0:13:04.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I won't let you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.23,0:13:08.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't treat us like ingredients\nfor your Sacred Jewel!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.27,0:13:10.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes... Priestess!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.14,0:13:10.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.04,0:13:11.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Resist!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.97,0:13:14.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And make your spirit even\nstronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.71,0:13:18.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Only vultures will come near\nthis abominable body!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.95,0:13:20.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Birds take flight at the sight\nof me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.02,0:13:23.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and flowers wilt from my breath!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.49,0:13:24.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sick of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.49,0:13:32.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,With the power of the Sacred Jewel,\NI will grasp all things beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.76,0:13:34.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then your wish is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.60,0:13:38.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I will become human with\nthe Sacred Jewel,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.83,0:13:40.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and abandon this soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.44,0:13:43.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.41,0:13:49.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.25,0:13:52.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.61,0:13:55.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.00,0:14:14.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You cannot get away, Kagome.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.94,0:14:16.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.14,0:14:19.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.17,0:14:20.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome! You're okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.51,0:14:24.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, everyone!\NStay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.88,0:14:26.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome, we're here to rescue you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.56,0:14:38.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.39,0:14:39.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.10,0:14:48.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shippo, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.10,0:14:49.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shippo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.44,0:14:55.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kirara!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.68,0:15:00.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.86,0:15:15.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.97,0:15:22.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.25,0:15:35.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.05,0:15:40.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So this is their hideout!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.89,0:15:42.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha! More of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.04,0:16:03.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who's next?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.55,0:16:14.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What're you doing?!\NGo and weaken him more!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.12,0:16:17.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,B-But... Orochidayu is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.56,0:16:21.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Orochidayu is dead!\NNow obey me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.96,0:16:23.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shut up, half-demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.43,0:16:25.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Half-demon?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.07,0:16:29.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're just a half-demon,\nyet you dare order us around!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.97,0:16:32.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Since Orochidayu is gone,\NI will be!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.18,0:16:37.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Gama... take his soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.25,0:16:39.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.21,0:16:40.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hurry it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.89,0:16:47.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn bull! So you're behind all this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.79,0:16:50.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And you, a half-demon, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.16,0:16:54.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, whatever...\njust come at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.66,0:16:58.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Get him!\NAnd you'll get a Sacred Jewel!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.07,0:17:02.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wind Scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.58,0:17:11.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please, let everyone go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.41,0:17:13.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.65,0:17:16.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I need their souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.18,0:17:18.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And yours as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.82,0:17:20.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And which soul do you have now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.72,0:17:24.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Izumo? Or Gyu-oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.56,0:17:28.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My soul is now within chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.90,0:17:33.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's why with the Sacred Jewel,\NI will obtain a human soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.90,0:17:36.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you're going to kill us\nin the process,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.77,0:17:38.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,you can't become human!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.21,0:17:40.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.11,0:17:44.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Sacred Jewel will be tarnished\nby your greed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.38,0:17:46.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.69,0:17:55.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,With the Sacred Jewel, I can become\nan undefiled human being!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.33,0:17:59.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Izumo! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.29,0:18:00.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please stop this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.23,0:18:05.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even if you appear as Gyu-oh,\nyour soul can still remain Izumo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.60,0:18:06.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.98,0:18:14.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Izumo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.51,0:18:18.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I will abandon this appearance!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.98,0:18:23.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.92,0:18:25.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Enough already!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.45,0:18:26.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.79,0:18:31.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Your courage is absolutely\nnecessary to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.66,0:18:35.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And in order to get you,\NI will do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.60,0:18:40.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.71,0:18:53.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I WILL create a real\NSacred Jewel!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.35,0:18:56.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You are one stubborn bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.89,0:19:01.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Everyone, hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.66,0:19:05.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.36,0:19:10.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't you detest your\nhalf-demon appearance?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.17,0:19:12.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't deny it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.50,0:19:16.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Half-demon! Half-demon!\NWill you stop harping on that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.94,0:19:18.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.87,0:19:20.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,As long as I'm strong,\NI don't care what I look like!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.74,0:19:21.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.78,0:19:23.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.55,0:19:25.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wind Scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.95,0:19:31.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Sacred Jewel!\NI need the Jewel!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.79,0:19:33.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.59,0:19:37.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Before day breaks,\NI need the Sacred Jewel!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.36,0:19:41.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wake up, Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.57,0:19:44.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.85,0:19:57.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.18,0:19:59.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.08,0:20:00.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't shine yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.38,0:20:02.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hear me, oh Sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.68,0:20:04.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I am going to change my destiny!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.12,0:20:06.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Rejected by humans...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.82,0:20:09.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even demons wouldn't accept me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.22,0:20:12.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All because I was born\na half-demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.69,0:20:15.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So what of it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.87,0:20:18.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Quit complaining!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.37,0:20:26.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And make something\nof yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.35,0:20:34.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.79,0:20:42.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.42,0:20:43.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.69,0:20:47.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Give this Gyu-oh just a few\nmore moments!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.66,0:20:51.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please, oh Sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.33,0:20:54.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.87,0:20:56.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The imitation Sacred Jewel...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.75,0:21:05.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How I regret it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.01,0:21:06.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.78,0:21:09.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Izumo was the half-demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.79,0:21:14.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He was Gyu-oh at night.\NAnd a human during the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.56,0:21:18.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The miasma in the imitation\NSacred Jewel was too toxic for humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.16,0:21:23.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.70,0:21:27.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Am I going to be able to die\nas a human?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.28,0:21:39.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Izumo...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.75,0:21:45.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.72,0:21:47.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.90,0:22:02.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey! What's the matter, Kagome?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.34,0:22:05.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nothing. Be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.28,0:23:49.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.54,0:23:51.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The miasma has gone inside my body...\nthe toxic poisons!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.78,0:23:54.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Jaken has been stung by\NNaraku's toxic insects!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.55,0:23:56.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We have to find the\nantidote flower!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.72,0:23:57.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Or Jaken's life is in!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.79,0:23:59.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hear me, Rin.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.39,0:24:02.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have been blessed to accompany\NLord Sesshomaru on his travels.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.72,0:24:05.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have no regrets in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.13,0:24:07.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, Jaken! Don't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.83,0:24:11.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next on Inuyasha:\N"Jaken Falls Ill"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.03,0:24:15.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh dear... is this really\nthe end?
